#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.208"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.208:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.208:0.2"
msgid "21. Sappurisavagga"
msgstr "21. A Good Person"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: dutiyapāpa-kalyāṇasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.208:0.3"
msgid "208. Dutiyapāpadhammasutta"
msgstr "208. Bad Character (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.208:1.1"
msgid "“Pāpañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, pāpena pāpatarañca;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you who’s bad and who’s worse,"

msgctxt "an4.208:1.2"
msgid "kalyāṇañca, kalyāṇena kalyāṇatarañca."
msgstr "who’s good and who’s better."

msgctxt "an4.208:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha … pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.208:2.1"
msgid "“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pāpo?"
msgstr "And who’s bad?"

msgctxt "an4.208:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco micchādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … micchāñāṇī hoti, "
"micchāvimutti hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong "
"knowledge, and wrong freedom."

msgctxt "an4.208:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpo."
msgstr "This is called bad."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.208:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pāpena pāpataro?"
msgstr "And who’s worse?"

msgctxt "an4.208:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca micchādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca "
"micchādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti … pe … attanā ca micchāñāṇī hoti, parañca "
"micchāñāṇe samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong "
"knowledge, and wrong freedom. And they encourage others in these same "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an4.208:3.3"
msgid "attanā ca micchāvimutti hoti, parañca micchāvimuttiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.208:3.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpena pāpataro."
msgstr "This is called worse."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.208:4.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kalyāṇo?"
msgstr "And who’s good?"

msgctxt "an4.208:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sammādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … sammāñāṇī hoti, "
"sammāvimutti hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right "
"knowledge, and right freedom."

msgctxt "an4.208:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kalyāṇo."
msgstr "This is called good."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.208:5.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kalyāṇena kalyāṇataro?"
msgstr "And who’s better?"

msgctxt "an4.208:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca sammādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca sammādiṭṭhiyā "
"samādapeti … pe … attanā ca sammāñāṇī hoti, parañca sammāñāṇe samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right "
"knowledge, and right freedom. And they encourage others in these same "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an4.208:5.3"
msgid "attanā ca sammāvimutti hoti, parañca sammāvimuttiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.208:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kalyāṇena kalyāṇataro”ti."
msgstr "This is called better.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.208:5.5"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
